## Success Criteria
- ✅ Link strength calculated based on connection count
- ✅ Edges rendered with variable stroke-width (1-5px)
- ✅ Search bar filters and highlights matching nodes
- ✅ Highlighted nodes gold color, larger size, thick border
- ✅ Non-highlighted nodes/edges dimmed during search
